<div data-controller="appear">
  <h1 class="type-serif-heading text-center animate-fade-in-up" style="font-size: var(--text-3xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Attire</h1>
  <p class="type-serif-small text-center animate-fade-in-up delay-1" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
    Black Tie Optional
  </p>

  <div class="card appear" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
    <div class="card-body text-center">
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); max-width: 36rem; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
        A polished, contemporary interpretation of black tie. Think modern silhouettes, elevated fabrics and understated evening elegance.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    <section class="card appear">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Formal Wear</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
          Floor-length gowns or refined evening attire in luxurious, warm-weather fabrics. As portions of the celebration will unfold outdoors, we recommend footwear suited to terraces, gravel paths and garden terrain.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card appear appear-delay-1">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Suits & Tuxedos</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
          Traditional black tie or tailored eveningwear. Lightweight tuxedos or summer-weight tailoring are ideal for warm weather, paired with polished accessories for a distinguished finish.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card appear appear-delay-2">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Cultural Attire</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
          Cultural and traditional attire is warmly welcomed for those who wish to wear it — formal dress in keeping with the evening is perfectly appropriate for the occasion.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>
